quitter le bureau

00:29:48.460 --> 00:29:49.080
demain.

00:29:49.700 --> 00:29:50.240
Donc,

00:29:51.300 --> 00:29:52.140
arrête de m'éviter,

00:29:52.920 --> 00:29:53.420
d'accord?

00:30:00.720 --> 00:30:01.280
Je ne le ferai pas.

00:30:03.400 --> 00:30:03.840
Vraiment?

